# Secrets and auth
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
!**/.env.template
**/auth.json
**/*token*
**/*secret*
**/*credentials*
**/*cookies*
**/twitter_cookies.txt

# Runtime/session state (do not back up)
**/sessions/
**/state.db
**/state.db-*
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
**/*.db
**/*.db-*
**/gateway.pid
**/gateway_state.json
**/.restart_last_processed.json
**/.tick.lock
**/channel_directory.json
**/logs/
**/*.log
**/tmp/

# Source clone / vendored deps (rebuild on restore)
**/hermes-agent/
**/node_modules/
**/__pycache__/
**/.pytest_cache/
**/*.pyc
**/*.pyo
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/

# OS/editor noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo

# Lock files created at runtime
**/*.lock
!**/package-lock.json
!**/poetry.lock
!**/uv.lock
